name.en,en_AU: Save Ins Comment - Export Ins Comments
name.en_GB,en_US: Save IG Comment - Export IG Comments

short.ar: سيساعدك هذا الامتداد على تصدير تعليقات Instagram أو حفظها بسرعة إلى ملف XLS / CSV.
short.am,bg,bn,ca,da,de,el,et,fa,fi,fil,gu,he,: This extension will help you quickly export or save Instagram comments to XLS/CSV file.
short.cs: Toto rozšíření vám pomůže rychle exportovat nebo uložit komentáře Instagramu do souboru XLS/CSV.
short.en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US: This extension will help you quickly export or save IG comments to XLS/CSV file.
short.es,es_419,ro: Esta extensión lo ayudará a exportar o guardar rápidamente los comentarios de Instagram en un archivo XLS/CSV.
short.fr: Cette extension vous aidera à exporter ou à enregistrer rapidement les commentaires Instagram dans un fichier XLS/CSV.
short.nl: Met deze extensie kun je Instagram-opmerkingen snel exporteren of opslaan in een XLS/CSV-bestand.
short.no: Denne utvidelsen vil hjelpe deg med å eksportere eller lagre Instagram -kommentarer til XLS/CSV -filen.
short.tr: Bu uzantı, Instagram yorumlarını hızlı bir şekilde XLS/CSV dosyasına aktarmanıza veya kaydetmenize yardımcı olacaktır.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_GB,en_US,e:
This extension will help you quickly export or save ins comments to XLS/CSV file for free.

🎉 Best Instagram tool made for people who want to export comments from Instagram into CSV.

⚙️ How to export comments?
① Open the instagram page.
② Click the "Export" button.

🔒 Data Privacy
All data is processed in your local computer, it is never passing through our web server, no one knows what you exported.
long.en,en_AU:
This extension will help you quickly export or save ins comments to XLS/CSV file for free.

🎉 Best IG tool made for people who want to export comments from Instagram™ into CSV.

⚙️ How to export comments?
① Open the IG page.
② Click the "Export" button.
